==Description== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:3-->
The [[File:Spreadsheet_AlignBottom.svg|24px]] '''Spreadsheet AlignBottom''' tool aligns the text inside a cell to the bottom of the cell.

==Usage== <!--T:4-->

<!--T:5-->
# Make sure there is an active [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|spreadsheet]].
# Select a cell.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_AlignBottom.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_AlignBottom|Align bottom]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Spreadsheet → Alignment → [[File:Spreadsheet_AlignBottom.svg|16px]] Align bottom}} option from the menu.


